All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Booster
    This is the super-class of all boosters.
    BoosterEffect
    The BoosterEffect is a shell around a Booster with a timer which times its duration.
    BoosterId
    This is a list of all objects in our game to reference their type.
    CircularSaw
    A circular saw is an enemy that always turns left.
    Coin
    The coin class simply provides points for the player when picked up.
    Difficulty
    This class keeps tracks of difficulty by spawning new enemies as the player's score increases past the threshhold.
    Enemy
    Class that contains all basic structure of the two enemies: CircularSaw and Zombie Makes sure sub-classes set damage and stay out of the walls
    FlashBomb
    This booster slows all enemies to .5 speed for 5 seconds, then resets the speed back.
    Game  
    HealthBar
    Class for the players Health.
    HUD
    Class for the Heads Up Display the HUD shows the players health HUD.HealthBar, the amount of coins the player has picked up and the booster that is active.
    Item
    This class is the super-class of all boosters and coins that can be picked up by the player.
    Maze
    This is our TileMap; It generates our only level and gives map-related information to other objects.
    ObjectSpawner
    This class creates all game objects and spawns them in the map.
    Player
    This is the class for the player.
    PlayerSpawnTile
    This is an empty tile that serves to mark the spot to spawn the player.
    SawSpawnTile
    This is an empty tile that servers to mark the spots to spawn new circular saws.
    SpeedBoost
    This booster increases the player's speed to 4 for 5 seconds, then resets it.
    StartingDifficulty
    Class for Starting Difficulty The starting difficulty gives a value based on the users input.
    WallTile
    This is the wall tile that is impenetrable to players and enemies.
    Zombie
    Class for the zombie This enemy tries to follow the player and cannot go through walls.
